                  <triggerstring n="disp">bestätigt</triggerstring>, dass ihm sein <rs type="fn" role="recipient"><rs type="person" ref="#pe__martin_QGW_II_I_1264"><roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__dietrich_urbetsch_QGW_II_I_1192">Schwager</roleName> Mert, <roleName type="occ" corresp="#org__bruenn">münzmaister</roleName> ze Brünn</rs></rs>, zu
